caption.p: Effects of Litsea cubeba, garlic, and Curcuma longa oil inhalations on positive and negative moods; happy, serene, lethargic, and stress. p value compared Litsea cubeba oil with garlic oil: ns ≥ 0.05, * < 0.05, and **** < 0.0001. p value compared Curcuma longa oil with garlic oil: not significant (ns) ≥ 0.05, # < 0.05, and #### < 0.0001.
